How to use linkedlist and arraylist

When we just add or remove its elements，we use linked list
however if we use lots of queries，we better use the array list。

How to use aslist method。
arrays.aslist is a kind that inner class of arrays. It is radically not a class
Instance of java.lang.arraylist.
Also it do not have the method of add or remove.
We have to new the arraylist agsin and use the arrays.arraylist as its constrictor parameter.

